quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,7,woh tumahray liye boojh dho (Lad) kar aisay aisay maqamat taq le jatay hain jahan tum sakht jaanfishani ke baghair nahi poanch satke haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab bara hi shafeeq aur meharban hai
16,8,uss ne ghoray aur khachar aur gadhay peda kiye taakay tum un par sawaar ho aur woh tumhari zindagi ki ronaqe banin woh aur bohat si cheezein ( tumahray faiday ke liye ) peda karta hai jin ka tumhe ilm taq nahi hai
16,9,aur Allah hi ke zimma hai seedha rasta batana jab ke rastay tirhhe bhi mojood hain agar woh chahta to tum sab ko hadaayat day deta
16,10,wohi hai jis ne aasman se tumahray liye pani barsaya jis se tum khud bhi sairaab hotay ho aur tumahray janwaron ke liye bhi charah peda hota hai
16,11,woh is pani ke zareya se khityan ugata hai aur Zaitoon aur khajoor aur angoor aur terhan terhan ke dosray phal peda karta hai iss mein aik barri nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
16,12,uss ne tumhari bhalai ke liye raat aur din ko aur Sooraj aur chaand ko maskhar kar rakha hai aur sab tarre bhi usi ke hukum se maskhar hain iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain
16,13,"aur yeh jo bohat si rang barang ki cheezein is ne tumahray liye zameen mein peda kar rakhi hain, inn mein bhi zaroor nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo sabaq haasil karne walay hain"
16,14,wohi hai jis ne tumahray liye samandar ko maskhar kar rakha hai taakay tum is se taro taaza gosht le kar khao aur is se zeenat ki woh cheezein nikalu jinhein tum pehna karte ho tum dekhte ho ke kashti samandar ka seenah cheertihui chalti hai yeh sab kuch is liye hai ke tum apne rab ka fazl talaash karo aur is ke shukar guzaar bano
